dialog.text:
Whaaaaat?! I'm sorry! Start the...SBS-san.
{{-}}
[[File:SBS73 1 Gasu Gasu Fart.png|thumb|right|300px|Left: Dad; Bottom: Me]]

Those are farts! FARTS! It's "Henokuni" (VIZ: "Land of the Farts"). 
{{-}}
[[File:SBS73 1 Law's Tattoos.png|right|100px]]

Yes! Robin loves Chopper, so she always keeps some of his favorite candy around to give to him at any time!
{{-}}
[[File:SBS73 2 Montblanc Cricket.png|right|150px]]

I don't think about girls the way you do. It's nothing but serious bustiness--ahem, business--in there. And you're right about Luffy's train of thought! I guess he only remembered the rhythm of the name.
{{-}}
[[File:SBS73 2 Aremo Ganmi.png|right|150px]]

I hear you! It sets my heart racing. You think, "When is your wardrobe malfunction?!" You might wonder why she'd wear such a skimpy outfit, but there's that pesky weight limit. I don't want to draw her that way, I swear. Come on! Come on!
{{-}}
[[File:SBS73 3 Wapol.png|right|120px]]

It gets better.
{{-}}
[[File:SBS73 3 Sanji Kicked in Groin.png|right|150px]]

Not remembering their names won't affect your ability to understand the story. If I don't make a character's name clear enough through the story, it's not an important of a name to begin with. This answer ate a whole page though!

Well, it's time. That's another SBS in the can! See you next volume!
{{-}}
